description: Stricter rules for config, infrastructure, and high-risk secret leakage paths
globs: "**/.env*,**/docker-compose*.yml,**/docker-compose*.yaml,**/*.tf,**/*.tfvars,**/values.yaml,**/.github/workflows/*.yml,**/.gitlab-ci.yml,**/helm/**/values*.yaml"
alwaysApply: false
